Class BusTravellerMovement.ContinueBusTripDecider

  • java.lang.Object
    • movement.BusTravellerMovement.ContinueBusTripDecider
  • Enclosing class:
    BusTravellerMovement

    class BusTravellerMovement.ContinueBusTripDecider
extends java.lang.Object
    Small class to help nodes decide if they should continue the bus trip. Keeps the state of nodes, i.e. how many stops they have passed so far. Markov chain probabilities for the decisions. NOT USED BY THE WORKING DAY MOVEMENT MODEL
    Author:
    Frans Ekman
